            <title>[LUCENE-1272] Support for boost factor in MoreLikeThis</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1272</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a patch I made to be able to boost the terms with a specific factor beside the relevancy returned by MoreLikeThis. This is helpful when having more then 1 MoreLikeThis in the query, so words in the field A (i.e. Title) can be boosted more than words in the field B (i.e. Description).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
